description:
From the deep forests and treacherous marshes they came, a small band of Polish partisans led by ex-cavalry office and a British agent who was half-Polish himself. Their clothes were ragged, their weapons an assortment which would make any regular quartermaster wince.

But they all had one thing in common - a burning desire to fling the Nazis out of their Polish homeland. That made them as deadly and dangerous as the name they had chosen for themselves - The Fighting Eagles.
name: Fighting Eagles

description: The war was over but Jimmy Fisher's Thunderbolt pilots were still dying in battle... All because of a few Japanese pilots who fought on in a fanatical hunt for glory. Jimmy could be a fanatic too, though - as these Japs were about to find out!
name: Too Late For Glory?

description: One of the few comics that have true Steampunk themes. This short but sweet Grant Morrison graphic novel that collect the 1993 3-issue miniseries from Vertigo tells of a remarkable young man that chooses to live his life above even the most resplendent gentlemen in this alternate history take on 1895 England . Sebastian O is an ego centric character that you can't take your eyes off and with the action, mystery, and intrigue that is contained within this collection it feels a natural fit for any fans of Grant Morrison or comic books like League Of Extraordinary Gentlemen. Also note that the 3 pages of alternate historical timeline that Grant spins at the beginning of the story are equally as enthralling as the story itself.

Lieutenant Sammy Parker had seen no action at all - for he was in the Pay Corps and had spent most of his army career sitting behind a desk in a quiet office in Burma.

But now it was different. The Japanese were advancing, driving everything before them, so Sammy was on the run and fighting for his life. More and then - there was a bunch of soldiers depending on him too.

Would he make it, this young office who had never been in such a desperate situation in his whole life?

First published 1980
name: Last Man Out

description:
Havok, Nova, Captain Ultra...Shocker, Plantman, Batroc the Leaper - not the Defenders, but TWO incredible simulations! But the debacle of the dozens of 'Defenders for a Day' is just the start for the latest look at Earth's Mightiest Non-Team! Will they be driven mad by Lunatik, or blown away by Foolkiller? International crises and extradimensional warfare abound! The secret of Omega the Unknown! Asgardians, androids and guys with wings on their heads! Plus: Spider-Man, the Black Panther and a guest-appearance by Millie the Model!

Collecting DEFENDERS #61-91.

description: Juanito gathers around him many warriors in order to rid the territory of the garimpeiros which at one time belonged to his tribe. Also Mister No who by chance finds himself in that zone risks death. But the repression of the army follows very harsh
name: Lampi di Battaglia

description: At Manaus three Indios are looking for the man with the four leaf clover on his arm : they want to kill him to fulfil the revenge which Mister No cannot explain. The reason will come to him in a livid dawn of blood
name: Caccia Spietata

description: New El Dorado is a new mining city which has sprung up in the middle of the Peruvian jungle. Esse-Esse has gone down there to look for work as a policeman in the private police force of the city, but finds only trouble ! In fact, when Mister No lands at New El Dorado , a bitter surprise awaits him: Esse-Esse has disappeared and maybe he has been killed
name: Un Amico in Pericolo
A Copa Na Avenida

description: There is corruption at New El Dorado and Mister No will realize this by investigating upon the mysterious disappearance of Esse-Esse. But who could be interested in eliminating him ? His police colleagues ? The contrabandists who steal the gold from the mine ? His own company ? The answer is unforeseeable, as no one is what they seem to be in New El Dorado Three fugitive criminals cross the path of Mister No and for Jerry there is no escape
name: La Sfida del Gringo

description: Lucho Oliveira, nick-named The Indio, is such a ruthless and bloody bandit that he merits the name Terror of the Rio Negro Now he has escaped from prison and wants to reach the hide-out of his band hidden in the forest. It will be exactly Mister No, against his will, to support the escape and to help kidnap the young daughter of a very rich land owner but a squad of policemen are on their track
name: Il Terrore del Rio Negro

description: Mister No and Marilena Moraes Da Costa, the daughter of a very rich land owner, are hostages of the pirates, without any possibility of escape from their inaccessible refuge. There seems to be no way out of the situation and the only person who might be able to save them is the traitor who hides among the pirates: an infiltrated policeman . But Romao, the relentless leader of the group, suspects something Presentation: Its time for settling the accounts at the nest of the Condor, the hide-out of Lucho Romao, The Terror of the Rio Negro
name: Nel Covo dei Pirati

description: Mindy, the former artiste of the Flying Circus, has married the millionaire John Knox, whos about to open some new industrial premises in Amazonia as one more of his many companies. But the joy at this homecoming is destined to be short-lived, because blistering-hot lead is going to scorch the nights of Manaus
name: Morte a Manaus
Como Mudar Uma Casa

description: The trip into the heart of the jungle turns out to be full of insidious hazards, and not just because of the dangers that lurk in the Amazon forest, but above all because an unsuspectable enemy is prowling around and weaving his plot behind the scenes against Knox, and therefore also against Jerry Drake and the friends who are traveling with him...
name: LOmbra dello Scorpione

description: Mister No and Esse-Esse bring a supply of medicines to the fazenda of Marcelo Santos, where their doctor friend Gilbert Brel works. But something mysterious is going on inside the strip mine owned by Santos, where numerous Indios are forced to toil mercilessly. And the murderous fury of the slaves that breaks out during the night proves to be unstoppable
name: I Dannati della Miniera

description: The former slaves of the La Cruz mine arent going to stop until theyve driven every single white man out of their forest! Barricaded in the fazenda, Mister No, Esse-Esse, Brel, Santos, Elisa and a group of mercenaries find themselves having to face a night of pure hell
name: LAssedio

description: Gambling debts can cost you dearly, especially if the winning cards are in the hand of a scoundrel like Suerte! Mister No is thus forced once again to risk life and limb and venture out with his Piper into the Andes of Columbia, in search of Ramn Uriaga, a gangland boss whose life is in danger unless someone brings him his medication. But after a hair-raising death-defying landing, Jerry Drake discovers that Uriaga conceals a dramatic secret
name: Avventura sulla Cordigliera

description: The dramatic escape staged by Mister No and Uriaga, the Columbian crime heavy whos decided to turn states evidence, develops into an absolutely lethal flight. The new crime bosses De Medeiros and Cordeiro cannot allow the pair to get to their rendez-vous with the police alive. Also, the baddies are extremely numerous and very heavily armed, and to defeat them Mister No will have to play a wily game
name: Due Vite in Gioco
Copa Ou Cozinha?
